'''Thembi Mtshali-Jones''' (yavutse 7 Ugushyingo 1949), ni umukinnyi wa filime wo [[Afurika y’Epfo|muri Afurika yepfo]] .  Ufatwa nk'umwe mu bahanzi bazwi cyane muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] y'Epfo, Thembi azwiho kuba afite uruhare mu biganiro byinshi bya televiziyo bizwi cyane nka ''Sgudi 'Snaysi'', ''Stokvel'', ''Umutangabuhamya'' ''ucecetse'' na Imbewu.  Usibye gukina, ni n'umuririmbyi uzwi cyane, umwanditsi w'amakinamico akaba n'umuhanzi wungirije ushinzwe kwigisha muri Global Arts Corps muri Kosovo ndetse n'umutoza muri Kamboje.

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse ku ya 7 Ugushyingo 1949 i Sabhoza, umudugudu uri hafi ya Ulundi, Durban, Afurika y'Epfo .  Ababyeyi be baratandukanye nyuma gato yo kuvuka kwe.  Nyuma yaje gukurira mu mujyi wa KwaMashu aho yarangirije amashuri ye.  Mu gihe cy’ishuri, yarasamye bityo ahatirwa kuva ku ishuri. 

Mu 1998, yigaga muri kaminuza ya Gallaudet i Washington DC, muri [[Amerika]] nyuma aza muri kaminuza ya Louisville, muri Amerika mu 2004. Umusanzu mu bijyanye n'ubuhanzi, yagizwe umuturage w'icyubahiro wa Louisville na Meya maze ahabwa amajwi yo gushimira na Sena ya Kentucky . Nyuma guverineri wa Kentucky yamuhaye izina rya Cyubahiro Kentucky Colonel, icyubahiro cyinshi muri Kentucky. 

== Umwuga ==
''Impano'' ye yo gukina yavumbuwe na Welcome Msomi aho Thembi yakoreye muri Umabatha yumwimerere. Nyuma yinjiye muri 'Musical Ipi Tombi', maze aba umugore wambere nka 'Mama Tembu'. Yakoze ingendo mpuzamahanga nyinshi zirimo West End na Broadway . Nyuma yaje kujya muri [[Amerika]] kuzamura umwuga we wa muzika aho yahuye nabacuranzi bakunzwe Hugh Masekela na Miriam Makeba .  Bazengurutse u Burayi na [[Afurika]] imyaka myinshi. Mu 1987, Thembi yagarutse muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] y'Epfo yinjira mu Isoko ry'ikinamico. Ku ikinamico, yabonye amahirwe yo gukorana na Janice Honeyman muri Black Follies. 

Mu Gushyingo 2019, Thembi yahawe igihembo cyitwa The Living Legend Award mu iserukiramuco ry’amakinamico ry’abirabura ryabereye muri Carolina y'Amajyaruguru, muri [[Amerika]] kugira ngo atandukanye serivisi yakoreye sinema yo muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] y'Epfo.  Muri uwo mwaka, yakinnye mu bicuruzwa byamamaye cyane ''Mama kuri Mama'' mu iserukiramuco ry’imikino ry’abirabura. Ikinamico yari ishingiye ku gitabo cyanditswe na Sindiwe Magona .   Nyuma Magona yanditse igitabo kivuga ku mibereho 'Theatre Road: Inkuru yanjye ni inkuru ishishikaje ya Thembi Mtshali-Jones', yasohotse kugira ngo ihure n'imyaka 70 ya Mtshali-Jones. 

